# Generated data assets (rebuild with `npm run data`).
# Most are regenerated in CI from committed results/ tables, so stay ignored.
# EXCEPT predictions/: their source CSVs are too heavy to commit (~5MB each), so
# the small downsampled prediction JSON are committed and CI keeps them as-is.
public/data/*
